# Tests that a graph can be created, four nodes and
# edges from one node to the other three can be added, 
# and four nodes and three edges can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing2

# Add four nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing2 Bilbo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing2 Gandalf
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing2 Arwin
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing2 Samwise

# Add three edges from Bilbo to different children
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing2 Bilbo Gandalf TheHobbit
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing2 Bilbo Arwin TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing2 Bilbo Samwise TheTwoTowers

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Bilbo
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing2
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing2 Bilbo